==Written work==

#{{cite book|title=Thal<U+00ED>a : <U+00A1>Belleza! Lessons in Lipgloss and Happiness|date=September 6, 2007|publisher=[[Chronicle Books]]|isbn=0811858294}}
#{{cite book|title=Thal<U+00ED>a: <U+00A1>Radiante! Your Guide to a Fit and Fabulous Pregnancy|date=April 1, 2009|publisher=[[Chronicle Books]]|isbn=081185812X}}
